  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Banished and striped of free will...</h2><strong>As a punishment from the gods, you were trapped high up on some floating islands. Get ready for the ultimate card-based roguelite game</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/37e6a5f9f0e67133095949d409052ba6.poster.avif?t=1712770976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/37e6a5f9f0e67133095949d409052ba6.webm?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/37e6a5f9f0e67133095949d409052ba6.mp4?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Show guidance.</u><br>Forge ahead to new islands, emboldened by the treasures you uncover in the chests along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/e847195949e9e3b0dbfdaf6a3e8b84ff.poster.avif?t=1712770976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/e847195949e9e3b0dbfdaf6a3e8b84ff.webm?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/e847195949e9e3b0dbfdaf6a3e8b84ff.mp4?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Unlock new cards.</u><br>Unlock new cards by completing challenges and pleasing the gods.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/0b3c038c58618ef5158c2d18b9da54f1.poster.avif?t=1712770976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/0b3c038c58618ef5158c2d18b9da54f1.webm?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/0b3c038c58618ef5158c2d18b9da54f1.mp4?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Gather.</u><br>Gather food, resources, potions and equipment to help you on your journey of survival.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/232cfd1a2312390047b36b5b3006c3a1.poster.avif?t=1712770976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/232cfd1a2312390047b36b5b3006c3a1.webm?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/232cfd1a2312390047b36b5b3006c3a1.mp4?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Battle monsters.</u><br>The gods didn't leave you alone. They maliciously placed evil creatures to try and take your chance at freedom. Rise to the challenge and show your strength as the alpha predator of this realm.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/16036126cb561360e2205d1b8cb1f4ac.poster.avif?t=1712770976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/16036126cb561360e2205d1b8cb1f4ac.webm?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/16036126cb561360e2205d1b8cb1f4ac.mp4?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><u>Make it through the night</u><br>Drink a potion, eat a banana and take a break next to the campfire. The night is not the best time to go exploring the islands as many of its strongest inhabitants are nocturnal... and hungry!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/9091d13eb5c0e703144143da8154714d.poster.avif?t=1712770976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/9091d13eb5c0e703144143da8154714d.webm?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2750200/extras/9091d13eb5c0e703144143da8154714d.mp4?t=1712770976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
